{"tid":2321197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國對美國宣戰？《彭博》北京記者「危害國安」遭逮捕","createTime":"2020-12-11T10:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T13:55:22.000Z","uid":337052,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7da0c8ae8fa4bacb0310b5ff42eb2f5753b59630","tid":2321197,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"疑涉參與「危害國家安全活動」《彭博》駐北京女記者被捕<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/11/phpxSmSiM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2FphpxSmSiM.jpg&h=68011eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美媒《彭博》今報導，中國以「危害國家安全」為由，逮捕一名彭博駐北京新聞辦公室的女記者范海茲（Haze Fan，音譯），對此，中國官方回應，目前這起案件仍在調查中。（圖擷取自推特）<br />\n<br />\n2020/12/11 18:19<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美媒《彭博》今（11日）稍早報導，中國以「危害國家安全」為由，逮捕一名彭博駐北京新聞辦公室的女記者范海茲（Haze Fan，音譯），對此，中國官方回應，目前這起案件仍在調查中。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，范海茲在7日上午11點半在和彭博的編輯同事聯絡後，就遭數名便衣公安從住處帶走。<span class=\"red\">《彭博》為此多次向中國政府與中駐美大使館詢問相關消息，直到昨（10）收到消息，范海茲被控涉嫌「參與危害國家安全」的活動而被逮捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n《彭博》發言人表示，他們非常關注此事件，會持續積極與中國政府對話，「在掌握更多訊息的同時，我們也正持續盡一切努力幫助她」。對此，中國官方回應稱，目前這起案件仍在調查中，范海茲的合法權利會得到充分保障，也提到她的家人已經收到通知。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，范海茲是中國公民，她在2017年開始擔任《彭博》記者，在此之前曾為CNBC、CBS、半島電視台及路透等國際媒體工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3378782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3378782&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmlxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=7d2b0f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3378782&h=6e8496fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3378782</a>"},{"pid":"9045a3be4e24024cbf6f8c4e3ddfb71355eee451","tid":2321197,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Chinese Authorities Detain Bloomberg News Beijing Staff Member</span></strong><br />\nBy Reto Gregori and Madeleine Lim<br />\n2020年12月11日 下午5:00 [GMT+8]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/chinese-authorities-detain-bloomberg-news-beijing-staff-member\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-12-11%2Fchinese-authorities-detain-bloomberg-news-beijing-staff-member&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmlxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=21cf84e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-11/chinese-authorities-detain-bloomberg-news-beijing-staff-member</a>"},{"pid":"671911876738938ef8b74fb72b238a8dde1287db","tid":2321197,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美國彭博新聞社中國女記者被指涉危害國安 在北京被拘留</span></strong><br />\n2020-12-11<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美國彭博新聞社週五(11日)報導，中國當局以涉嫌危害國家安全為由，拘留了其北京分社記者Haze Fan。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導說，Haze Fan在當地時間週一上午11:30左右失聯，其後被目擊由便衣人員押送出寓所。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，<span class=\"red\">Haze Fan失踪四天以來，彭博新聞社一直通過中國政府和中國駐華盛頓大使館尋找其下落。週四彭博新聞社母公司彭博社收到消息，證實Haze Fan由於涉嫌參加危害國家安全的活動而被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導說，Haze Fan是中國公民，於2017年開始在彭博新聞社工作，歷任多家外媒。而根據規定，中國公民只能擔任外國新聞機構的新聞助理，不得進行獨立報導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul1211c-12112020051033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul1211c-12112020051033.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmlxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=09388c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul1211c-12112020051033.html</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n報導引述中方官員指，Haze Fan正被拘留於北京市國家安全局，並稱其合法權利得到了充分保障，她的家人已得到通知。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n記者 呂熙 責編 胡力漢"},{"pid":"f58cbfb84fad1138e1d690e5fcb47ce499d83b1b","tid":2321197,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201211/2000x1500_0704228111977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20201211%2F2000x1500_0704228111977.jpg&h=0641a09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭博社11日發出聲明表示，北京辦公室的中國籍雇員范若伊（前）7日遭便衣執法人員帶走。（<a href=\"http://圖取自twitter.com/Hazeology\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAtwitter.com%2FHazeology&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmlxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=e95f8066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自twitter.com/Hazeology</a>）"},{"pid":"70af470f89bd1c03b16b7390e7907897e71625cb","tid":2321197,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"竟然係彭博？ <br />\n<br />\n《彭博新聞》引述報告報導指，研究結果反映，病毒在美國出現的時間，比科學家和衞生官員已知的還要早幾個星期，進一步提供了證據，表明病毒在中國通報首個病例的幾個星期之前，已在全球蔓延，亦重燃關於病毒源頭的爭論。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博新聞》指出，美國的發現並非首次顯示武肺病毒早於2020年已在中國以外出現感染者。一名法國病人在12月尾因流感症狀入院治療，其後發現感染武漢肺炎，明顯與官方說法相牴觸。根據法國政府的數據顯示，武肺病毒是在1月底，由19個從武漢回法國的旅客所傳入。"},{"pid":"149e420f535533e6d9a303ccc02e24fa3dfd545f","tid":2321197,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"又拉左報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4d4b391ae100f51097119c4e2f43234b6a219d","tid":2321197,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"只係識搞自己人"},{"pid":"976fc02678fb8a06cfcfd77e4ca1d00fbed19243","tid":2321197,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4d4b391ae100f51097119c4e2f43234b6a219d","tid":2321197,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"只係識搞自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"不敢抓美國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c79780733469da7c1fe53b9e57f2f69add71083","tid":2321197,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor